# API Automation Project Structure

This is a Java-based API automation framework using Cucumber, RestAssured, and Maven with support for multiple API suites.

## Project Structure

- **Main Framework**: [pom.xml](mdc:pom.xml) - Maven project with dependencies
- **Test Features**: Three separate feature repositories based on executionBase configuration
- **Step Definitions**: [src/test/java/com/Bizom/stepDefinitions/](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/stepDefinitions/) - Shared Java step implementation classes
- **Utilities**: [src/main/java/com/Bizom/commonUtils/](mdc:src/main/java/com/Bizom/commonUtils/) - Common utility classes
- **Test Data**: [src/test/resources/InputData/](mdc:src/test/resources/InputData/) - JSON/XML test payloads
- **Runners**: [src/test/java/com/Bizom/runner/](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/runner/) - TestNG runners for each API suite

## Multi-Suite Architecture

The framework supports three distinct API suites with separate feature repositories:

### 1. BizomWebAPI Suite
- **Feature Path**: [src/test/java/com/Bizom/BizomWebAPI/feature/](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/BizomWebAPI/feature/)
- **Runner**: [BizomWebAPI_Runner.java](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/runner/BizomWebAPI_Runner.java)
- **TestNG Config**: [BizomWebAPI_Testng.xml](mdc:src/test/resources/NG_XMLs/BizomWebAPI_Testng.xml)
- **Base URI**: `bizomWebApiBaseUri=https://devuitest.bizomdev.in/`
- **Tags**: `@BizomWebAPI`

### 2. IntegrationAPI Suite
- **Feature Path**: [src/test/java/com/Bizom/IntegrationAPI/feature/](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/IntegrationAPI/feature/)
- **Runner**: [IntegrationAPI_Runner.java](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/runner/IntegrationAPI_Runner.java)
- **TestNG Config**: [IntegrationAPI_Testng.xml](mdc:src/test/resources/NG_XMLs/IntegrationAPI_Testng.xml)
- **Base URI**: `integrationApiBaseUri=https://devapi.bizomdev.in/`
- **Tags**: `@Execution`

### 3. RetailerAPI Suite
- **Feature Path**: [src/test/java/com/Bizom/RetailerAPI/feature/](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/RetailerAPI/feature/)
- **Runner**: [RetailerAPI_Runner.java](mdc:src/test/java/com/Bizom/runner/RetailerAPI_Runner.java)
- **TestNG Config**: [RetailerAPI_Testng.xml](mdc:src/test/resources/NG_XMLs/RetailerAPI_Testng.xml)
- **Base URI**: `retailerApiBaseUri=` (configurable)
- **Tags**: `@Execution`

## Execution Configuration

### executionBase Parameter
Users must specify the `executionBase` parameter to determine which API suite to execute:
- `executionBase = WebApi` → Executes BizomWebAPI suite
- `executionBase = Integration` → Executes IntegrationAPI suite  
- `executionBase = Retailer` → Executes RetailerAPI suite

### Feature File Organization
- Features are organized by API modules within each suite (Users, Orders, Sales, etc.)
- Each module contains GET/POST feature files
- Naming convention: `{HTTP_METHOD}_{API_NAME}.feature`

### Step Definitions (Shared)
- `GetSteps.java` - GET request step definitions
- `PostSteps.java` - POST request step definitions  
- `ApiRequestModificationSteps.java` - Request modification and validation steps
- `ApiResponseValidationSteps.java` - Response validation steps
- `DBValidationSteps.java` - Database validation steps
- `DeleteSteps.java` - DELETE request step definitions
- `PatchSteps.java` - PATCH request step definitions
- `PutSteps.java` - PUT request step definitions

### Resource URIs
- [src/main/java/com/Bizom/commonUtils/ResourceURIS.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/Bizom/commonUtils/ResourceURIS.java) - Centralized endpoint definitions
- Endpoints mapped by request name keys (e.g., "zones_add", "subzones_add")

### Test Data
- JSON payloads in [src/test/resources/InputData/](mdc:src/test/resources/InputData/)
- XML payloads for specific APIs
- Configuration in [src/test/resources/Configurations/config.properties](mdc:src/test/resources/Configurations/config.properties)